<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>2022-10 on</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/tags/2022-10/</link><description>Recent content in 2022-10 on</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 10 Oct 2022 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://yshghid.github.io/tags/2022-10/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>끄덕끄덕일기</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2022/22blog22/</link><pubDate>Mon, 10 Oct 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2022/22blog22/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="끄덕끄덕일기"&gt;
 끄덕끄덕일기
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%eb%81%84%eb%8d%95%eb%81%84%eb%8d%95%ec%9d%bc%ea%b8%b0"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2022. 10. 10. 00:21&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="2275" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/b6ce21c9-ac4c-4d23-a362-b7555e8a498f" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이수업은 좋으면서 싫고 먼가 애매..! 들으러가는길은 자유롭고 좋은데 들을때는 너무 고통스럽고 눈앞이흐려짐 근데 마치고 집가는길에는 날아갈것같다&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이날 박태준 카페탐험기 봤는데 진짜재밌었어서 더좋았다&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e27049ec-7d1b-42f0-9bc5-aef3547c08a3" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이날 되게알차게 뭔가를했는데 뭘했는지는 기억안나네
스벅에서 빵시켜먹으면 기분 좋음&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/425f64cc-b635-48ae-8c1e-2acaf4a93fe6" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이날 엄마랑 민이랑 시내가서 마제소바 먹고 자라에 쇼핑도 갔다&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="960" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/7bf9335f-a287-41d3-add4-e5b7cad7a8bb" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이날은 할머니 할아버지랑 브런치먹으러갔다&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1840" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/9cfd694f-7340-41a3-87e4-3a07adea7b33" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;스켑틱을 집중잘될때에 읽으면 너무너무 행복함&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2aa1dda3-3f22-4434-9fbf-a83b7f5bbbaa" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;기분애매할때는 편의점에서 라면이나 과자 털이&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/047f2432-a8e3-468e-81c5-6fb8e09cb7f0" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이날 기분 안좋을필요 없었던데&amp;hellip; 아쉽다 안좋았던거 뭔가 발표준비안된거같아서 기분별로였는데 그래서그냥 하다말고 나왔는데 연구실사람들을 만나서 커피도사주시고 이래저래해져서 나아졌다&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>살아있는 한, 네 마음 가는대로 해라</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/daily/daily39/</link><pubDate>Mon, 10 Oct 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/daily/daily39/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="살아있는-한-네-마음-가는대로-해라"&gt;
 살아있는 한, 네 마음 가는대로 해라
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%ec%82%b4%ec%95%84%ec%9e%88%eb%8a%94-%ed%95%9c-%eb%84%a4-%eb%a7%88%ec%9d%8c-%ea%b0%80%eb%8a%94%eb%8c%80%eb%a1%9c-%ed%95%b4%eb%9d%bc"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2022-10-10&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://m.blog.naver.com/afx1979/222854957281"&gt;https://m.blog.naver.com/afx1979/222854957281&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;img width="1214" height="1064" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/283d783a-8f0c-42d4-a347-d8d495309f91" /&gt;
&lt;img width="1232" height="1152" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/05d2f2d1-72fa-4285-aab2-e71678b5e720" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;네 마음 가는대로와 네가 하고 싶은 대로의 차이. 내 마음이 향하는 곳을 알려면 아주 찬찬히 들여다보아야함. 들여다보는것의 결과는?
내가 하고싶다고 생각하는 것들 중에서 사회에 의해 학습된 것 / 내가 생물학적으로 인간이기 때문에 내의지와 상관없이 원하게 되는 것&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;을 제외시킬수있음.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="860" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/bb23876b-324d-410b-ac3d-acfec8eb1e8d" /&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1463" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3ef1deda-ab89-49d4-a8b5-8f39b404da2a" /&gt;</description></item><item><title>혼돈 속 메시지</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/daily/daily40/</link><pubDate>Wed, 05 Oct 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/daily/daily40/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="혼돈-속-메시지"&gt;
